==English==
===Etymology===
From [[Greek]] ''[[Euphorbus]]'', a [[Trojan]] [[surgeon]] mentioned in the ''[[Iliad]]''.

===Noun===
'''Euphorbia'''
#Large, [[cosmopolitan]] [[genus]] of [[flower]]ing [[plant]]s, and basis for the name of the plant family [[Euphorbiaceae]]. Individual species in the genus may grow as [[herb]]s, [[shrub]]s, or [[tree]]s, but all typically have [[latex]] and paired [[spine]]s.

